{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "ai-service-seatnow-2026",
		"name": "SeatNow - AI Service",
		"description": "Test collection for SeatNow AI Service (port 3007).\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Redis Caching Layer:** High-performance data caching for restaurants, user history, and admin analytics (< 1ms data retrieval).\n- Public AI: Guest recommendations (No Auth required)\n- Customer AI: restaurant recommendations + multi-turn chat\n- Admin AI: revenue analytics + business strategy chat\n\n**Setup:** Fill in `customerToken` and `adminToken` in the Variables tab before running tests.\n\nGet tokens via: POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/login",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:3007",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "customerToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "JWT access token for a customer account (role=customer). Get from auth-service login."
		},
		{
			"key": "adminToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "JWT access token for an admin account (role=admin). Alternatively use internal token: vhTony_24_internal_token"
		},
		{
			"key": "ownerToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "JWT access token for a restaurant owner account (role=restaurant_owner)."
		}
	],
